node.text:
Climate change is a HUGE problem . Lots of ppl don’t know it affects communities w Black , Indigenous , and People of Color a lot more than whiter neighborhoods .

Today I'm Super excited to launch the @TAZO Tree Corps!! 🤗 With ur help we'll plant 🌲🌲🌲 in five US cities to fight the effects of climate change. That way we can help EVERYBODY gain access to better air/water , mental health , and lower (!!) utility bills ✨

Go to bit.ly/TAZOTreeCorps and apply before 3/12 !* #TAZOPartner #TAZOTreeCorps

*Applicants for this year’s Tree Corps must be 21+, located in Detroit, Minneapolis, or the San Francisco Bay Area, and interested in working outdoors. Selected applicants will be invited by The Davey Tree Expert Company to participate in a paid training program before transitioning into full-time employment. Check out the full list of requirements at bit.ly/DaveyTreeCorps

node.title: TAZO x SZA launch the TAZO Tree Corps
